== Reception ==
As with the earlier CRL adventures ''[[Dracula (1986 video game)|Dracula]]'', ''[[Frankenstein (adventure game)|Frankenstein]]'', and [[Jack the Ripper (adventure game)|''Jack the Ripper'']], the game was classified by the [[British Board of Film Censors]], receiving an [[18 (British Board of Film Classification)|'18' certificate]] for its gory graphics.<ref>[https://bbfc.co.uk/releases/wolfman-1970 BBFC rating report on Wolfman]</ref><ref name="zzap">{{cite journal | last = Wilde| first = Nik | title = Adventure - Wolfman Review| journal = [[Zzap!64]]| issue = 37| pages = 38, 39| publisher = [[Newsfield Publications]]| date = May 1988}}</ref>

